<collectingCountry box="[1122,1226,1523,1548]" name="Tanzania" pageId="26" pageNumber="227">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
. Two of them are deposited in NHMW, and the third male specimen collected from 
<collectingCountry box="[885,1006,1559,1583]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="26" pageNumber="227">DR Congo</collectingCountry>
is preserved in RMCA. The male 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,1560,1584]" pageId="26" pageNumber="227">type</typeStatus>
in RMCA was dissected and the genitalia are illustrated here.
</paragraph>
